❌ Problem

You used:

oc cp bscf/bscf125-bpp0-5bb84c8c88-bvj8g:/root/vpms_noti.pcap ./home/srib/kamal/

👉 ./home/srib/kamal/ is treated as a relative path, not the actual /home/srib/kamal/

So it tried to copy into:

~/kamal/home/srib/kamal/

(which doesn’t exist → file not copied)


